data.title: Thailand in The 2010's
data.meta_description: Thailand in the 2010's - Free ebook download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or read book online for free. Ten years into the 21st century, this publication showcases Thailand's progress and development. The first decade saw great changes in socioeconomic terms with the country striving to uphold the principles of a "sufficiency economy" in response, successive governments have developed strategies to drive forward education, social security, justice, defence, environmental protection and health.
